{"id":39,"date":"2021-03-30T07:44:18","date_gmt":"2021-03-30T06:44:18","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/barchessa-loredan.local\/?page_id=39"},"modified":"2021-04-19T07:53:28","modified_gmt":"2021-04-19T06:53:28","slug":"filosofia","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"http:\/\/barchessa-loredan.local\/identita\/filosofia\/","title":{"rendered":"Filosofia"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<div class=\"wp-block-cover alignfull has-background-dim hero-section\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" class=\"wp-block-cover__image-background wp-image-155\" alt=\"\" src=\"http:\/\/barchessa-loredan.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/alasdair-elmes-QTgOjDCiJEo-unsplash-1024x683.jpg\" data-object-fit=\"cover\" srcset=\"http:\/\/barchessa-loredan.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/alasdair-elmes-QTgOjDCiJEo-unsplash-1024x683.jpg 1024w, http:\/\/barchessa-loredan.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/alasdair-elmes-QTgOjDCiJEo-unsplash-scaled-600x400.jpg 600w, http:\/\/barchessa-loredan.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/alasdair-elmes-QTgOjDCiJEo-unsplash-300x200.jpg 300w, http:\/\/barchessa-loredan.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/alasdair-elmes-QTgOjDCiJEo-unsplash-768x512.jpg 768w, http:\/\/barchessa-loredan.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/alasdair-elmes-QTgOjDCiJEo-unsplash-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, http:\/\/barchessa-loredan.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/alasdair-elmes-QTgOjDCiJEo-unsplash-2048x1365.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><div class=\"wp-block-cover__inner-container\">\n<h1 class=\"has-text-align-center\">Filosofia<\/h1>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-left hero-highlight\">\u201cIn ogni bottiglia del nostro vino c\u2019\u00e8 rispetto per la terra.<br>C\u2019\u00e8 un vino mai uguale a se stesso che nasce tra i vigneti e si affina in cantina.<br>Ci sono tecniche antiche mischiate a pratiche innovative.<br>C\u2019\u00e8 una squadra che lavora con passione.\u201d<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns are-vertically-aligned-center\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center\">\n<h2>Qualit\u00e0 autentica<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Siamo convinti che il vino si faccia\/nasca in vigna e non in cantina. Tra i vigneti inizia e si concentra gran parte del nostro lavoro.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ricerchiamo costantemente, attraverso la cura dei vigneti, la miglior qualit\u00e0 delle uve, per poter raggiungere un\u2019autentica qualit\u00e0 finale del vino.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" src=\"http:\/\/barchessa-loredan.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/kelsey-knight-udj2tD3WKsY-unsplash-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-158\" srcset=\"http:\/\/barchessa-loredan.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/kelsey-knight-udj2tD3WKsY-unsplash-1024x683.jpg 1024w, http:\/\/barchessa-loredan.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/kelsey-knight-udj2tD3WKsY-unsplash-scaled-600x400.jpg 600w, http:\/\/barchessa-loredan.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/kelsey-knight-udj2tD3WKsY-unsplash-300x200.jpg 300w, http:\/\/barchessa-loredan.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/kelsey-knight-udj2tD3WKsY-unsplash-768x512.jpg 768w, http:\/\/barchessa-loredan.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/kelsey-knight-udj2tD3WKsY-unsplash-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, http:\/\/barchessa-loredan.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/kelsey-knight-udj2tD3WKsY-unsplash-2048x1365.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns my-6 bg-light p-2 rounded border\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column separator-r-skin\">\n<svg class=\"md-icon icon-shadow icon-bg-skin-dark mb-05\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\">\n    <path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M14 12C14 13.1 13.1 14 12 14S10 13.1 10 12 10.9 10 12 10 14 10.9 14 12M7 10C5.9 10 5 10.9 5 12S5.9 14 7 14 9 13.1 9 12 8.1 10 7 10M17 10C15.9 10 15 10.9 15 12S15.9 14 17 14 19 13.1 19 12 18.1 10 17 10M14.5 6C13.4 6 12.5 6.9 12.5 8S13.4 10 14.5 10 16.5 9.1 16.5 8 15.6 6 14.5 6M9.5 6C8.4 6 7.5 6.9 7.5 8S8.4 10 9.5 10 11.5 9.1 11.5 8 10.6 6 9.5 6M14.5 14C13.4 14 12.5 14.9 12.5 16S13.4 18 14.5 18 16.5 17.1 16.5 16 15.6 14 14.5 14M9.5 14C8.4 14 7.5 14.9 7.5 16S8.4 18 9.5 18 11.5 17.1 11.5 16 10.6 14 9.5 14M12 18C10.9 18 10 18.9 10 20S10.9 22 12 22 14 21.1 14 20 13.1 18 12 18M14.4 2.2L13.6 1C11.4 2 11.2 5.6 11.2 6H12.7C12.8 5.2 13.1 2.7 14.4 2.2Z\"><\/path>\n<\/svg>\n\n\n\n<p>Preferiamo aver una minor resa per ettaro alla produzione massiva, sostenendo la qualit\u00e0 alla quantit\u00e0.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column separator-r-skin\">\n<svg class=\"md-icon icon-shadow icon-bg-skin-dark  mb-05\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\">\n    <path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M3,13A9,9 0 0,0 12,22C12,17 7.97,13 3,13M12,5.5A2.5,2.5 0 0,1 14.5,8A2.5,2.5 0 0,1 12,10.5A2.5,2.5 0 0,1 9.5,8A2.5,2.5 0 0,1 12,5.5M5.6,10.25A2.5,2.5 0 0,0 8.1,12.75C8.63,12.75 9.12,12.58 9.5,12.31C9.5,12.37 9.5,12.43 9.5,12.5A2.5,2.5 0 0,0 12,15A2.5,2.5 0 0,0 14.5,12.5C14.5,12.43 14.5,12.37 14.5,12.31C14.88,12.58 15.37,12.75 15.9,12.75C17.28,12.75 18.4,11.63 18.4,10.25C18.4,9.25 17.81,8.4 16.97,8C17.81,7.6 18.4,6.74 18.4,5.75C18.4,4.37 17.28,3.25 15.9,3.25C15.37,3.25 14.88,3.41 14.5,3.69C14.5,3.63 14.5,3.56 14.5,3.5A2.5,2.5 0 0,0 12,1A2.5,2.5 0 0,0 9.5,3.5C9.5,3.56 9.5,3.63 9.5,3.69C9.12,3.41 8.63,3.25 8.1,3.25A2.5,2.5 0 0,0 5.6,5.75C5.6,6.74 6.19,7.6 7.03,8C6.19,8.4 5.6,9.25 5.6,10.25M12,22A9,9 0 0,0 21,13C16,13 12,17 12,22Z\"><\/path>\n<\/svg>\n\n\n\n<p>Prediligiamo metodi e tecniche che rispettino l\u2019ambiente e l\u2019uomo, riducendo al minimo l\u2019utilizzo dei fitofarmaci.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\">\n<svg class=\"md-icon icon-shadow icon-bg-skin-dark  mb-05\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\">\n    <path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M4.5,11A1.5,1.5 0 0,0 6,9.5A1.5,1.5 0 0,0 4.5,8A1.5,1.5 0 0,0 3,9.5A1.5,1.5 0 0,0 4.5,11M22.17,9.17C22.17,5.3 19.04,2.17 15.17,2.17A7,7 0 0,0 8.17,9.17C8.17,12.64 10.69,15.5 14,16.06V20H6V17H7V13A1,1 0 0,0 6,12H3A1,1 0 0,0 2,13V17H3V22H19V20H16V16.12C19.47,15.71 22.17,12.76 22.17,9.17Z\"><\/path>\n<\/svg>\n\n\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">Studiamo costantemente nuovi metodi innovativi, come il metodo di potatura Simonit &amp; Sirch, che asseconda la naturale attitudine della vite.<\/span><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns are-vertically-aligned-center offset-hor my-6\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" src=\"http:\/\/barchessa-loredan.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/kelsey-knight-udj2tD3WKsY-unsplash-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-158\" srcset=\"http:\/\/barchessa-loredan.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/kelsey-knight-udj2tD3WKsY-unsplash-1024x683.jpg 1024w, http:\/\/barchessa-loredan.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/kelsey-knight-udj2tD3WKsY-unsplash-scaled-600x400.jpg 600w, http:\/\/barchessa-loredan.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/kelsey-knight-udj2tD3WKsY-unsplash-300x200.jpg 300w, http:\/\/barchessa-loredan.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/kelsey-knight-udj2tD3WKsY-unsplash-768x512.jpg 768w, http:\/\/barchessa-loredan.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/kelsey-knight-udj2tD3WKsY-unsplash-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, http:\/\/barchessa-loredan.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/kelsey-knight-udj2tD3WKsY-unsplash-2048x1365.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" src=\"http:\/\/barchessa-loredan.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/maja-petric-vGQ49l9I4EE-unsplash-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-160\" srcset=\"http:\/\/barchessa-loredan.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/maja-petric-vGQ49l9I4EE-unsplash-1024x683.jpg 1024w, http:\/\/barchessa-loredan.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/maja-petric-vGQ49l9I4EE-unsplash-scaled-600x400.jpg 600w, http:\/\/barchessa-loredan.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/maja-petric-vGQ49l9I4EE-unsplash-300x200.jpg 300w, http:\/\/barchessa-loredan.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/maja-petric-vGQ49l9I4EE-unsplash-768x512.jpg 768w, http:\/\/barchessa-loredan.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/maja-petric-vGQ49l9I4EE-unsplash-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, http:\/\/barchessa-loredan.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/maja-petric-vGQ49l9I4EE-unsplash-2048x1365.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center p-1\">\n<h2>Processi naturali<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>In cantina il vino si affina e si perfeziona, ma quando arrivano le uve il pi\u00f9 del lavoro si \u00e8 gi\u00e0 compiuto. L\u2019aggettivo \u201cnaturale\u201d accompagna i processi messi in atto dal nostro enologo.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Naturali sono i lieviti utilizzati.<\/li><li>Naturali i processi di raffreddamento delle vasche sfruttando l\u2019ambiente interno e la posizione della nostra cantina, situata dentro la Barchessa.<\/li><li>Non correggiamo i vini ed \u00e8 per questo che le annate di uno stesso nostro vino non saranno mai uguali.<\/li><li><strong>Solforosa (???)<\/strong><\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Infine, non ci spaventa l\u2019attesa, forse perch\u00e9 abbiamo ricavato una cantina dentro un edificio storico che ha atteso secoli prima di trasformarsi in quello che potete ammirare oggi.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p> &hellip;<\/p>\n<p class=\"read-more\"> <a class=\"\" href=\"http:\/\/barchessa-loredan.local\/identita\/filosofia\/\"> <span class=\"screen-reader-text\">Filosofia<\/span> Leggi tutto \u00bb<\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":34,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":""